OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FEarly fog clearing to leave a
OL,6,Fhot and sunny day across the country.
OL,7,FLight winds and high UV levels
OL,8,Fexpected. A very warm evening and
OL,9,Fnight to come too.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FStaying
OL,12,Fdry, sunny and very warm throughout.
OL,13,FThe wind picking up a little may just
OL,14,Fallow it to feel not quite as hot for
OL,15,Fmost. Nights remaining warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
